imitate_insert()

Imitates person who using keyboard and writes different wrong parametrs(those, who create exeptions or loops in input) and then the right one.

imitate_right()

Imitates person who using keyboard and writes right parametrs(those, who dont create exeptions or loops in input).

imitate_wrong()

Imitates person who using keyboard and writes different wrong parametrs(those, who create exeptions or loops in input) and then the right one.
